snippet.title: The Holy Chalice Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
The Holy Chalice is a top down twin stick shooter roguelite based in the fantasy world. You will fight through a variety of arenas and enemies to claim the chalice back for your goblin clan. 

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1793680/The_Holy_Chalice/
